# Exemplo de Variáveis de Ambiente

## CI/CD (GitHub Actions + Docker Hub)

### Docker Hub (para publicar imagens)
DOCKER_USERNAME=seu_username_dockerhub
# Nota: DOCKER_PASSWORD deve ser configurado como Secret no GitHub
# Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → New secret

---

## API (.NET)

### Banco de Dados
ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=Server=localhost,1433;Database=OrderTrackingDb;User Id=sa;Password=YourStrong@Passw0rd;TrustServerCertificate=True;MultipleActiveResultSets=true

### RabbitMQ
RabbitMqSettings__HostName=localhost
RabbitMqSettings__Port=5672
RabbitMqSettings__UserName=guest
RabbitMqSettings__Password=guest
RabbitMqSettings__QueueName=orders-queue

### ASP.NET Core
ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=Development
ASPNETCORE_URLS=http://+:8080

---

## Worker Service (.NET)

### Banco de Dados
ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection=Server=localhost,1433;Database=OrderTrackingDb;User Id=sa;Password=YourStrong@Passw0rd;TrustServerCertificate=True;MultipleActiveResultSets=true

### RabbitMQ
RabbitMqSettings__HostName=localhost
RabbitMqSettings__Port=5672
RabbitMqSettings__UserName=guest
RabbitMqSettings__Password=guest
RabbitMqSettings__QueueName=orders-queue

### .NET Environment
DOTNET_ENVIRONMENT=Production

---

## Frontend (React)

### API URL
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

---

## Docker Compose

Ao usar `docker-compose up`, as variáveis são automaticamente configuradas.
Para customizar, edite o arquivo `docker-compose.yml` ou crie um `docker-compose.override.yml`.

---

## Produção

⚠️ **IMPORTANTE**: Nunca commite credenciais reais no repositório!

Para produção:
1. Use Azure Key Vault, AWS Secrets Manager ou similar
2. Configure variáveis de ambiente no host/container
3. Altere senhas padrão (SA_PASSWORD, RabbitMQ credentials)
4. Use certificados SSL/TLS válidos
5. Configure CORS para domínios específicos

### Exemplo com User Secrets (Desenvolvimento Local)

```bash
# API
cd src/OrderTracking.Api
dotnet user-secrets set "ConnectionStrings:DefaultConnection" "SuaConnectionString"
dotnet user-secrets set "RabbitMqSettings:Password" "SuaSenha"

# Worker
cd src/OrderTracking.Worker
dotnet user-secrets set "ConnectionStrings:DefaultConnection" "SuaConnectionString"
dotnet user-secrets set "RabbitMqSettings:Password" "SuaSenha"
```
